# Portfolio Website Guidelines

## Design Principles
- Clean, minimal aesthetic that lets the architecture work speak for itself
- Large, high-quality images are the focus
- Easy navigation between projects
- Mobile-responsive design (looks good on phones and tablets)
- Fast loading times (optimize images)

## Tech Stack
This project uses simple HTML, CSS, and JavaScript:
- index.html - главная страница
- style.css - стили для всего сайта
- project-page.css - стили для страниц проектов
- script.js - интерактивность

## Project Structure
- Homepage with introduction and project grid
- Individual project pages in /projects folder
- Images stored in /images folder

## Image Handling
- Suggest appropriate image sizes (max 1920px wide for full-width, optimize for web)
- Use lazy loading for image galleries
- Support common formats: JPG, PNG, WebP
